Package br.com.ufs.orionframework.entitylamp

Class Lamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.ufs.orionframework.entitylamp.Lamp
  • public class Lamp
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to help to represent a JSON entity (FIWARE format) as object java. Here, to easy the developer's life. We've made a built-in Lamp entity, defined by: id, entitytype, name, location, radius. On other hand, the developer can create your own entity java and use orion to send, update etc.
    Since:
    1.0
